textAfterTable: Event Detail Information Event Detail Information Campus Forum on the Accreditation Process -- Please RSVP! Date Jan 29, 2014 Time 12:00 pm   Location PAC G Sponsor UIS Accreditation Team Views 2079 Originating Calendar HLC Accreditation UIS is pursuing institutional reaccreditation through the Higher Learning Commission (HLC) of the North Central Association of Colleges and Schools. To find out more about the reaccreditation process, meet members of the UIS accreditation team, and learn how you can participate in the campus reaccreditation efforts, please join us at this informational session. Schedule of Events: 12:00-1:00 p.m. - General information, question & answer session. 1:00-1:45 p.m. - Global Awareness and U.S. Communities instructors are welcome to stay for an additional informational session. Please RSVP by emailing accreditation@uis.edu if you plan to attend this event. Lunch will be provided to those who RSVP. If you are unable to attend, information regarding the accreditation process can be found at www.uis.edu/accreditation. link
